## SonarQube Rules — Python

### S3776 — Cognitive Complexity <= 15
Functions MUST NOT have Cognitive Complexity above 15. Extract logical blocks into private helper methods (`_method`). Use early returns to reduce nesting.

### S1192 — Duplicate strings
String literals MUST NOT be duplicated (3+ occurrences). Extract as module constant:

```python
# WRONG
Field(description="Message unique identifier")  # 3x

# CORRECT
_DESC_MESSAGE_ID = "Message unique identifier"
Field(description=_DESC_MESSAGE_ID)
```

### S1172 — Unused parameters
All function parameters MUST be used. If required by interface/Protocol but unused, prefix with `_` (e.g., `_name`, `_session`).

### S7503 — async without await
`async` functions MUST contain at least one `await`. If no async I/O, remove `async`. Exception: functions implementing an async Protocol/ABC.

### S2737 — Empty except
`except` blocks MUST NOT be empty. Add logging or re-raise:

```python
# WRONG
except Exception:
    pass

# CORRECT
except Exception:
    logger.warning("Operation failed", exc_info=True)
```

### S125 — Commented-out code
Commented-out code sections MUST be removed. If preservation needed, convert to issue/TODO with reference.

### S2068 — Hardcoded credentials
NEVER include passwords, tokens, or credentials directly in code. Use environment variables.

### S1135 — TODO comments
TODOs must reference an issue/ticket. Remove obsolete TODOs.

{{#if (eq module.stack "fastapi")}}
### S8396 — Pydantic: Optional with required default
Every `Optional[X]` or `X | None` field in Pydantic models MUST have `= None` explicit:

```python
# WRONG
field: Optional[str]

# CORRECT
field: Optional[str] = None
```

### S8409 — FastAPI: Don't duplicate response_model
When function has return type annotation, do NOT use `response_model=`:

```python
# WRONG
@router.post("/foo", response_model=FooResponse)
async def foo() -> FooResponse: ...

# CORRECT
@router.post("/foo")
async def foo() -> FooResponse: ...
```

### S8414 — CORSMiddleware must be last
CORSMiddleware MUST be added last in the FastAPI middleware chain (LIFO).
{{/if}}

